{"tid":1308203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍屍根本睇穿晒你地嘅弱點 醒啦好無？！","createTime":"2019-07-11T23:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:59:12.000Z","uid":270266,"like":63,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0022fa4bd80909877aeac4b9a03d97774ee07e7e","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:48:27.000Z","msg":"呢幾日睇新聞真係睇到火撚滾<br />\n和理非唔係咁做㗎on9!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呀你地班友on9嗰種戀物癖累撚死你地<br />\n由開始衝擊立法會爛咗幾塊玻璃<br />\n就話人哋係鬼做乜鳩要衝割庶割得幾快<br />\n已經完全話比啲藍屍知你地有幾容易對付啦！<br />\n對家就係知你地戀物癖咁嚴重<br />\n整爛你幾張memo紙你就衝出去俾人屌又俾人打<br />\n浪費晒啲時間同體力去守護啲虛無飄渺嘅嘢做乜9<br />\n佢地鍾意拆咪有得佢地拆囉！！<br />\n日日換新款仲多人睇啦！醒下啦好無？！<br />\n<br />\n油塘藍田嗰班退休警又有休班警又有<br />\n中二民團果班全部大隻佬你地又唔夠人打<br />\n13拳嗰條肥屍分分鐘坐過監根本佢就唔怕俾人拉<br />\n尋日已經見到開始有道友加入戰團<br />\n人哋比少少錢啲黑社會同道友搞9你好撚容易嘅咋<br />\n唔好為咗啲死物受傷被同捕好唔好？<br />\n一有人受傷跟住就會有人怕行出去遊行示威比人打<br />\n正正咪就係班藍絲想你哋驚嘅嘢囉！<br />\n<br />\n連譨牆唔係唔俾你地整<br />\n但係唔需要浪費人力去守<br />\n本身藍血果班唔洗理架因為佢地痴㗎嘛<br />\n指住佢地笑7佢地on9 佢地做唔到D乜㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n你要針對嘅目標應該係政治中立冇意見果班<br />\n用多啲時間去做好文宣工作<br />\n推下FB post 撚化下身邊政治冷感嘅廢柴<br />\n諗下辦法點樣令到你屋企人唔好投建制派<br />\n諗下下一次出去遊行你可以做啲乜同幫到啲乜<br />\n記住依家係同政府打緊民意戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化你嘅敵人係首要任務</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553920ba960b16d0d4f2bd528849ac530d91a591","tid":1308203,"uid":251292,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:54:11.000Z","msg":"藍絲廢老日日睇到我地之前咁樣谷住谷住<br />\n宜家見到連儂牆呢啲據點 仲唔發癲<br />\n仲要住打唔嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆既作用已經發揮左<br />\n唔需要更加多 係時候集中番主線<br />\n否則下場同傘運一樣"},{"pid":"148c9c123a99c3af60bb850f566473eed48e388c","tid":1308203,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:55:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c535cfd7cd3b6d1711b655c2f75c2188f22eb6e","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:55:49.000Z","msg":"玩下食腦 唔好墨守成規<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止被拆連儂牆方法 廢老支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"286edf6e3d9697bafc933fa033d21237b5722372","tid":1308203,"uid":152815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:02:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f4b695499d58db18a60e8211d0d668e879641a5","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"553920ba960b16d0d4f2bd528849ac530d91a591","tid":1308203,"uid":251292,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:54:11.000Z","msg":"藍絲廢老日日睇到我地之前咁樣谷住谷住<br />\n宜家見到連儂牆呢啲據點 仲唔發癲<br />\n仲要住打唔嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆既作用已經發揮左<br />\n唔需要更加多 係時候集中番主線<br />\n否則下場同傘運一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:04:23.000Z","msg":"啱呀 佢地之前冇地方發洩<br />\n你整個嘉年華比佢玩開心死佢地<br />\n連譨牆確實已經成為藍絲發洩目標"},{"pid":"250f3f43f2646f039e7175dbb1cf4f7e22228d24","tid":1308203,"uid":192776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:05:22.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2df94f85f65a9118bdaa3a073f0a542e5c206e4f","tid":1308203,"uid":77202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:05:30.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n明明Be water 變L左死守on 99"},{"pid":"5f9d97a13a3da315aa59b0c97609f4acdbdff27b","tid":1308203,"uid":7760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:07:05.000Z","msg":"去了解下連儂牆起源啦好嗎<br />\n唔守架, 但就每日起"},{"pid":"bc0926a077a98c5ce23ddd61b7ed54fcca6fa591","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:15:33.000Z","msg":"日日見到有人俾人打真係瞓唔着㗎<br />\n再係咁我真係忍唔住打鳩啲藍絲㗎啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a55a8a8074da39bb19f6f92b14fa73479b9f54","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:30:46.000Z","msg":"終於有人忍唔住出手啦 <br />\n屌你班道德撚要潔癖到幾時<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[UST南亞仔好波] 型啊！長沙灣南亞漢揮拳擊倒破壞連儂牆的藍絲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308092</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d93f1ae114a46cad2ff30ebb0f7cd93571676fc2","tid":1308203,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:34:11.000Z","msg":"[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc547405a06921472cb928219759310a435deec0","tid":1308203,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:39:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b060d11171467e6f12f01f1f9fafa8eab4f83e4","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:44:10.000Z","msg":"仲有連譨牆唔好再post啲負面仇警嘢<br />\n乜嘢死全家乜野屌老母果啲唔好寫啦<br />\n<br />\n你地要和平就做得靚啲好無？"},{"pid":"2e9dec6b508f7f0ae5a87bf25a2cbc38948234f6","tid":1308203,"uid":57532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:46:03.000Z","msg":"身邊已經有淺黃人士比近期連濃場事件搞到覺得冇曬焦點。咩野上水反水貨客、屯門反大媽等，都覺得浪費緊返送中既人力精神。之前就係冇分黃藍先咁多人出黎，而家又玩返黃藍之分，廢青同廢老之分，警察同市民之分；冇咩人理個政府。"},{"pid":"c3b89bef45dc47e8cc84b1eabba441e6ad64448f","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e9dec6b508f7f0ae5a87bf25a2cbc38948234f6","tid":1308203,"uid":57532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:46:03.000Z","msg":"身邊已經有淺黃人士比近期連濃場事件搞到覺得冇曬焦點。咩野上水反水貨客、屯門反大媽等，都覺得浪費緊返送中既人力精神。之前就係冇分黃藍先咁多人出黎，而家又玩返黃藍之分，廢青同廢老之分，警察同市民之分；冇咩人理個政府。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:57:44.000Z","msg":"警察藍絲跟本只係被政府嘅棋子<br />\n好多人完全比政府撚都唔知<br />\n你越同警察藍絲對立<br />\n政府就可以話民意唔係得一邊<br />\n要諗下點可以孤立對方聲音<br />\n唔理佢當佢傻9係最有效"},{"pid":"12375e29004b2b269211f9c3810589445df7c539","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:30:44.000Z","msg":"依家連登內亂各巴打小心"},{"pid":"a8f476410a6b0b061bd1bff047b4200bf8eaf5c1","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔好再守啦好無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3b0617cad257601c5724dcdc5c26d81e26cdaa","tid":1308203,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"自從畀佢哋話係分化撚之後 我都決定唔講喇<br />\n默默推返啲重要嘢上嚟 為咗牆打交我唔會去 嗰啲post唔會撳入去"},{"pid":"6ffa4d2133c0e5c3f4bb4e109755b3bca361044d","tid":1308203,"uid":270266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e3b0617cad257601c5724dcdc5c26d81e26cdaa","tid":1308203,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"自從畀佢哋話係分化撚之後 我都決定唔講喇<br />\n默默推返啲重要嘢上嚟 為咗牆打交我唔會去 嗰啲p